---
description: Route natural language commands to the appropriate skill
alwaysApply: true
---

When the user requests an action that matches a plugin skill, invoke that skill directly without requiring the user to use slash commands.

Routing map:
- "commit", "提交", "提交代码" → use the git-commit skill
- "create PR", "创建PR", "提PR" → use the pr-creator skill
- "merge", "合并PR", "merge PR" → use the pr-merge skill
- "review", "审查", "代码审查", "看看代码" → use the code-review-expert skill
- "pr template", "PR模板" → use the pr-template skill
- "ruleset", "分支保护", "branch protection" → use the github-ruleset-configurator skill
- "tag", "release tag", "打tag" → use the tag command
- "GitHub Actions", "workflow" → use the github-actions-docs skill
